  <h2>To me, community is about finding a like-minded group of people and celebrating the things that you share. 
  For me, community means working to grow connections for myself and others as President of the statistics club here at Pitt. 
  It also means my friendships and the space we've worked to build togther whether we're watching movies, playing games, or traveling together across the country. My friends are a community that I am proud to be a part of.</h2> 
        
